ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗諗下<br />\n其實佢價值觀同我好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一身鬆"},{"pid":"48ec0aad0d2b30f278f51426471c20e4895395c3","tid":411330,"uid":115397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:56:50.000Z","msg":"仲有6,70,年先死,，點等?<br />\n真心搵嗰個，好過啦<br />\n見人一對對又忍唔住"},{"pid":"f9e293f4f3a127abc910256f5556b0c52d9cfd7e","tid":411330,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有6,70,年先死,，點等?<br />\n真心搵嗰個，好過啦<br />\n見人一對對又忍唔住</blockquote><br />\n唔會忍唔住<br />\n只會由衷祝褔身邊嘅朋友<br />\n見到佢哋咁sweet自己都會開心埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a3be5c2c8af1e33c0ee6d41620a76a5100008a","tid":411330,"uid":24854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79dccefa0571c3cd9ac1c94b90713e9598212e5a","tid":411330,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>希望樓主遲下撞到好人個陣唔好hurt人就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一陣無限loop</blockquote><br />\n唔會hurt人<br />\n只會不斷提醒自己唔好認真</blockquote><br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家個男朋友好好 好想訓身去愛<br />\n但已經冇左呢個能力了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要唔好做對唔住佢嘅嘢就得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終有日你會愛上佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係咁中我ex伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacee5cc657a5d64eee8c2caee9282183d93b811","tid":411330,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T18:01:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e28c8c4ef746451c6d2996048337249852c5006","tid":411330,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep